**FIRE (Financial Independence, Retire Early)** is a lifestyle movement focused on building enough wealth to live off investment returns without traditional employment. The FIRE number is the corpus at which you can withdraw your annual expenses indefinitely (using a safe withdrawal rate). For Indian investors, this typically means 30–33× annual expenses given local inflation and return dynamics.
